      • contains

        boolean contains(java.lang.String key)
        Checks if the DataSet contains a named key.

        Checks each DataItem and sees if its key is the same as the named key.

        Parameters:
        key - A key for a DataItem.
        Returns:
        true if a DataItem exists with the named key, otherwise false.

      • put

        DataSet put(DataSet data)
        Put the contents of another DataSet into this one.

        Any items in the new data set that have a key that matches another item will overwrite the existing item.

        Parameters:
        data - The data to be added.
        Returns:
        the DataSet the item was added to.

      • remove

        DataItem remove(java.lang.String key)
        Removes the specified element from this DataSet.

        Returns:
